snippet.title: [Download] Star Revenge 6.9 - Luigi lost in Time - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Yet another hack by me, this time a smaller one, not as small as Temple Explorer or Seaside Town, but still only 25 stars to get. You can explore 3 new main courses and some side levels. It's normal difficulty (you know that that will never count for my bosses).
And no, I will never use that ugly skinny luigi model thingy, it's ugly.

Link: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qL_3tTQKWGao-lmqnDOjN5IfgcD4HJ5j/view

Music: ... non, Movie Maker said no to me adding music, so no music link :P
